Rambla del Mar



At the base of the rambla, this boardwalk led across the harbor to the MareMagnum shopping mall and the aquarium. Ahead is a swing-bridge to let the sailboats out of the marina to the left.
Taken Sunday, September 09, 2001, 03:07:45pm.  Original image size: 1600x1200, 1.0Mb
Technical details: Olympus C700UZ, 1/250s @ F6.3, ISO 100, 74mm
